{
  "texts": [
    "However, there are risks associated with the use of LLMs specifically that require special governance considerations, including privacy concerns.",
    "For example, any information used in the training of the LLM becomes part of how it learns and reacts in generating output.",
    "If confidential information has been used, it will be part of the system.",
    "Particularly, governance of LLMs should address privacy concerns (especially where a publicly available third-party LLM is being used), the handling of personal identifiable information or other sensitive information, and the validation of output.",
    "Given the lack of control over the output generated by the LLM, safeguards should be put in place to validate responses and to exclude any unethical discriminatory or hateful output."
  ]
}